---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
const updated = "March 25th 2025";
---

<BaseLayout brand="marysse" title="Privacy Policy">
  <section class="legal-page">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="legal-meta">Last updated: {updated}</p>

    <h2>1. Data Controller</h2>
    <p>
      This website is operated by Marysse (Maria Assunta Zangone),
      registered office at Via Lomellina 12, Milan (Italy).
      You may contact the data controller at
      <a href="mailto:info@maryssedesign.com">info@maryssedesign.com</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>2. Types of Data Collected</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Browsing data (technical and usage information collected through analytics tools).</li>
      <li>Contact data (name, email address and message content).</li>
      <li>Cookies and similar technologies (see Cookie Policy).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Purposes and Legal Basis</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Website analytics (legitimate interest).</li>
      <li>Handling contact requests (consent and/or pre-contractual measures).</li>
      <li>Website security and maintenance (legitimate interest).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
    <p>
      This website participates in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program.
      As an Amazon Associate, Marysse may earn from qualifying purchases.
      Affiliate links do not affect the final price paid by users.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
    <p>
      Personal data is retained only for as long as necessary to fulfil the purposes
      for which it was collected and in compliance with applicable laws.
    </p>

    <h2>6. User Rights</h2>
    <p>
      Users may exercise their rights under the GDPR, including access,
      rectification, erasure, restriction of processing, and data portability.
    </p>

    <h2>7. Updates</h2>
    <p>
      This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically. Users are encouraged
      to review this page regularly.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
